Bank representative ke janlam bollo somossa nai apnar sob complete joye geche. Next week er moddhe card peye jaben(evabe every week e shuni)

Then kichu din pore bollo NID sign ar bank sign er verify er jonne ekta form fillup korte seta dilam. 
Abar koyekdin age abar ekjon phone diye bole abar asbe verification a.but taake bollam amar card dorkar nai vai,sob process cancel kemne korbo NOC kmne pete pari seta bolen tao onekbar request korlo then abar aslo verification kore gelo physically.

Then akhn kalke abar ager same sign verification er form pathaise,sathe abaro amar bank Account verify korar jonne o form a sign chaise! Jekhane er age 2bar bank statement & verify korechilo setar jonne amar bank Account theke 115/- kore ketechilo protibar. 

Jar maddhome card processing korte diyechi taake text korlam, asb kemon drama kortesen bhai! Ak porjonto unar kono reply parlamNa. 

Next 2/1diner moddhe hoyto officially mail kore dibo. Card lagbena NOC er jonne. 

Ajaira pechal koira lav nai hudai.
